    {
      "id": "eed0bec0-cae4-4307-8e05-15aab4206190",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Authors develop a Semi-Supervised Learning Regression algorithm to predict the outcomes of undergraduate students. They carry out multiple tests to showcase the superiority of their method and conclude that they can obtain a MAE of 1.23 before the middle of the academic year. Authors also discuss implications for practice.  ",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "eed0bec0-cae4-4307-8e05-15aab4206190",
        "parent": {
          "type": "page_id",
